Document: VisualShaderNodeIf
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeif.rst
Summary: A visual shader graph node that outputs a 3D vector based on floating-point comparisons.

Inherits: VisualShaderNode < Resource < RefCounted < Object
Outputs a 3D vector based on the result of a floating-point comparison within the visual shader graph.
